    dc:description "Fig. 23. Georeferenced collection records of Lasioglossum (D.) eremum sp. nov. (black squares) and predicted distribution by maximum entropy ecological niche modelling in Maxent (colour shading). Warmer colours indicate higher cloglog probability of occurrence." ;
